Package: LimeSeed
Title: Use a structured YAML file as a survey source for LimeSurvey
Version: 0.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Stefan", "Munnes", , "munnes@wzb.eu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Avoid extensive manual clicking in the LimeSurvey web interface by creating and editing a user- and coding-friendly YAML file. This package converts that structured input into a format that can be imported directly into LimeSurvey to create a new survey. With this file-oriented approach, the full survey structure, content, and revision history remain part of your coding workflow.
